&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Electrical Engineering (BSEE) or equivalent engineering discipline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2-10 years of electrical engineering experience supporting production, manufacturing, or hardware development.&lt;/li&gt;
