&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role overview: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is for a hands-on technical leader to direct a gas turbine Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM) team driving design-to-build innovation and execution across a variety of methods from additive to related final machining. This role owns a variety of small gas turbine parts from concept to hardware. The focus is on speed, iterative design and ultimately scalable production.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Due to nature of these roles, applicants must be US Citizen and either hold or be willing to obtain a security clearance. This role is 100% onsite in either East Hartford, CT or West Palm Beach, FL. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Responsibilities: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
