&lt;li&gt;Design to Build Integration: Rapidly iterate designs, while closing the loop of design, build and test by feeding the learnings back into engineering at each stage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rapid Build &amp;amp; Iteration: Lead rapid build cycles like print→machine→inspect→build→learn, while collapsing timelines through iterations&lt;/li&gt;
