&lt;li&gt;Citizenship Requirement: Due to the nature of the work, all candidates must be U.S. Citizens.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Security Clearance: Due to the nature of the work, candidates must possess or be willing to obtain a DoD Secret/Collateral clearance.&lt;/li&gt;
